/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:19:41.000Z","msg":"食少野同食多野同勞碌命有咩關係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你唔想食多野所以不停逼自己做野？"},{"pid":"9598f3fd1cc80f99a95b7972900657d2dd822f63","tid":2338524,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01bc7efbcb94418c3b6fff8918176eed918b345f","tid":2338524,"uid":94266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6221bc78bd59b202768defbe33c6538998b1669","tid":2338524,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T03:57:33.000Z","msg":"如果有做嘢，食少少都飽<br />\n<br />\n不論食咩<br />\n<br />\n但一唔做嘢係度典玩訓就成日覺得食極唔飽<br />\n<br />\n係唔係勞碌命<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:19:41.000Z","msg":"食少野同食多野同勞碌命有咩關係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你唔想食多野所以不停逼自己做野？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T06:36:29.000Z","msg":"做嘢日子明明應該消耗大，食多啲<br />\n休息日子冇消耗，應該食少啲<br />\n<br />\n但我調轉<br />\n<br />\n感覺好冇效率<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"424ffbbac7f0dfc6de60a99484e639f9d9923a00","tid":2338524,"uid":16087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T08:39:35.000Z","msg":"冇做運動可以食少啲<br />\n廢事儲咁過量醣喺體內變脂肪"}]}